--- Test: Complex and Nested Comprehensions ---
--- Nested Comprehension (Matrix/Grid) ---
[[1, 2, 3], [2, 4, 6], [3, 6, 9]]
--- Nested List Comprehension with Variable Closure ---
[['x:1,y:1', 'x:1,y:2'], ['x:2,y:1', 'x:2,y:2']]
--- Complex Conditions in Comprehensions ---
[6, 8, 10]
--- Dict Comprehension with Multi-variable Unpacking ---
{'banana': 200, 'cherry': 300}
